bio: Expert guide specializing in cultural and historical tours across Sri Lanka. Passionate about sharing the rich heritage of the island with travelers from around the world. Fluent in multiple languages and certified by SLTDA.
Adventure tour specialist with extensive experience in wildlife safaris, hiking expeditions, and eco-tourism. Deep knowledge of Sri Lanka's national parks and biodiversity. Certified wildlife guide.
Coastal and beach tour expert covering the entire southern and western coastlines. Specializing in water sports, beach activities, and coastal heritage sites. Excellent communication skills.

Hill country and tea plantation specialist. Expertise in Nuwara Eliya, Ella, and the central highlands. Focus on nature trails, tea factory tours, and mountain trekking. Warm and friendly personality.

Ancient cities and UNESCO World Heritage site expert. Specializing in Sigiriya, Polonnaruwa, Anuradhapura, and Dambulla. Deep knowledge of Buddhist history and archaeology. Professional and knowledgeable.
